data.description: Charming One-Story home with 3 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, and a 2-Car Garage: This immaculate home near the Northern Hills Golf Course offers comfortable single-level living. The kitchen features granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, while the oversized backyard provides ample space for outdoor enjoyment. Benefit from energy savings with the 15-panel solar array on the roof. A vaulted ceiling in the living room, large windows, and a well-maintained interior complete this inviting package. Located in the highly sought-after North East Independent School District, this home is a must-see. Don't miss out-schedule a showing today!
